    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of March 25 T: Travel magazine article about resurgence of Dallas; Dallas Morning News's negative report on state of crime, schools and growth was published in 2004; improvements have been made in all areas since then</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on March 25 in T: Travel magazine, about the resurgence of Dallas, referred incorrectly to a negative report by The Dallas Morning News on the state of crime, schools and growth in Dallas. The report was published in 2004, not last year. Since then, some improvements have been reported in those areas. A reader pointed out the error in an e-mail message on April 9, and this correction was delayed for research.</p>
      </block>
